/california-flag-flies-in-the-turf-sprint |dead-url=no }}</ref>。炮彈在美國是首屈一指的草地短途馬，更在皇家雅士谷賽馬日有好表現，在[[金禧錦標|金禧錦標]]奪亞<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=Art Connoisseur Upsets Golden Jubilee Rivals |url=http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/51331/art-connoisseur-upsets-golden-jubilee-rivals |work= |publisher=bloodhorse.com |date=2009-06-20 |accessdate=2009-12-09 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202032/http://www.bloodhorse.com/horse-racing/articles/51331/art-connoisseur-upsets-golden-jubilee-rivals |dead-url=no }}</ref>。桂冠戰士今年比去年更進一步，2009年贏得短途一級賽[[高松宮紀念賽|高松宮紀念賽]]<ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |authorlink= |coauthors= |title=高松宮記念、ローレルゲレイロが念願のGI初制覇 |url=http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=35301&category=A |work= |publisher=netkeiba |date=2009-03-29 |accessdate=2009-12-05 |archive-date=2009-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331155752/http://www.netkeiba.com/news/?pid=news_view&no=35301&category=A |dead-url=no }}</ref>以及[[短途馬錦標|短途馬錦標]]<ref>{{cite news|first=|last=|author=下村靜史|coauthors=|script-title=ja:【スプリンターズＳ】ゲレイロ、１センチ差Ｖ|url=http://www.sanspo.com/keiba/news/091005/kba0910050511015-n1.htm|work=|publisher=[[產經體育|產經體育]]|date=2009-10-05|accessdate=2009-12-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091126022522/http://www.sanspo.com/keiba/news/091005/kba0910050511015-n1.htm|archivedate=2009-11-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |first= |last= |author= |coauthors= |script-title=ja:【スプリンターズＳ（ＧＩ）】（中山）～ローレルゲレイロ 激戦制して春秋スプリントＧＩ連覇 |url=http://keiba.radionikkei.jp/keiba/news/entry-173955.html |work= |publisher=[[日經廣播|日經廣播]] |date=2009-10-05 |accessdate=2009-12-06 |archive-date=2009-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091007035044/http://keiba.radionikkei.jp/keiba/news/entry-173955.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由南非轉投英國馬房的戰地畫家在德國及法國的分級賽有不錯的表現。

